schools.name: Southern School of Energy and Sustainability

data.description: Excellent open concept 3 bedroom home! Very charming and in a great Durham Location in popular Cardinal Oaks. Beautiful hardwood flooring on the main level,  fresh paint throughout the home, and a spacious island and kitchen perfect for entertaining. Commute easily to Duke University, RTP and Brier Creek. Less than 15 minutes to Downtown Durham, and less than 20 minutes to Falls Lake.
